				  <p>Are you sure you want to block this person?</p>
				  <p>Feel free to download the chat of their inappropriate/hurtful comments and send it to <a href="mailto:safespacebear@gmail.com">safespacebear@gmail.com</a> with the subject headline "PLEASE BLOCK USER PERMANENTLY."</p> 
			</div>

			<div class="modal-footer", data-dismiss="modal">
			    <%= link_to "Yes", friendship_path(:id => @other_user, block: true), method: :delete, class: 'btn btn-default' %>
